{"tid":1160882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"等習近平帶領既共產黨倒左台之後我會爆多一單共產黨機密","createTime":"2019-05-18T18:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T20:25:56.000Z","uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e4507c06e5cf29865b73a1ea4b961a107e782953","tid":1160882,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:27:18.000Z","msg":"絕不走數<br />\n點解一定要習氏共產黨倒台之後先可以爆呢<br />\n因為呢單機密係直接影響習近平可唔可以做到死為止<br />\n一爆撚左出黎，想習氏政權倒台都難<br />\n<br />\n唔係共產黨免費派華為手機比黨員，洗黨員腦叫黨員遠離iphone 呢d 碎料呀,係真係核彈級，影響中國命運既機密呀"},{"pid":"073bda53f3c5eb103cb99accc5a103313c906cd8","tid":1160882,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf1e09a591dcb324a2c7ef0112912e6271d5125","tid":1160882,"uid":110832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:29:36.000Z","msg":"唔好索野"},{"pid":"c8d74db53b34e0563b3845eaff358a1e473bd455","tid":1160882,"uid":167330,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"等樓主死撚咗之後我會爆單樓主老母嘅機密"},{"pid":"c1620ac0bd1c27992f1c83b7d6ba5d032a5ae8de","tid":1160882,"uid":199310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:38:38.000Z","msg":"爆咗死老母<br />\n<br />\n唔爆死全家"},{"pid":"e05ff6d23bdb037e3e4a138fd15bf553682077bf","tid":1160882,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8989b2efe8e1e3b4955ddb985ff6b0ddbc9e55c3","tid":1160882,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:03:20.000Z","msg":"呢單機密爆左出黎，對接替習近平既下一任共產黨員有一定影響<br />\n但如果係成個共產黨倒台，對新政府係零影響<br />\n就好似64同文革咁，你都唔會入新政府數啦<br />\n總之絕不走數啦<br />\n單小兒科碎料我都可以忍到大半年先爆<br />\n呢單核彈級勁料我係一撚定會忍到習帝倒左台之後先會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa1d9e632e3bc2f1d7e7d38e819eefa122152ed",